    {
      "id": "PopularPost183331",
      "post_content": "I run this is in an Izzetron alongside a [Molten Disaster](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Molten Disaster) and [Spell Burst](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Spell Burst) as my X spells. With Niv-Mizzet in the deck, it's soooo hard not to run this card for flavour alone. Plus, the ability to target creature, player, or draw cards has won me some games.  \n  \nI know I should probably use [Banefire](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Banefire) or something, but I can't seem to part with this!",
      "posted_by": "Kontrah",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost183331\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_post\">I run this is in an Izzetron alongside a <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Molten Disaster\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Molten Disaster\">Molten Disaster</a> and <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Spell Burst\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Spell Burst\">Spell Burst</a> as my X spells.  With Niv-Mizzet in the deck, it's soooo hard not to run this card for flavour alone.  Plus, the ability to target creature, player, or draw cards has won me some games.<br/><br/>I know I should probably use <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Banefire\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Banefire\">Banefire</a> or something, but I can't seem to part with this!</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"../../Classes/Controls/#\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '183331'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy67650\">Kontrah</span>\r\n                                (7/29/2011 12:17:41 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popula