      "id": "PopularPost206460",
      "post_content": "Nice card, and a lot of sinergy with [Niv-Mizzet](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Niv-Mizzet), obviously...! Maybe a cost of ![Variable Colorless](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=X&type=symbol)![Blue](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=U&type=symbol)![Red](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=R&type=symbol) wouldn't have made it overpowered, I think. Sadly, because I like it very much! Maybe if they had included a third choise, like \"or gain control of target creature with converted mana cost X or less.\", and ability that Blue and Red share, even if in red is only until end of turn but since there are 2 blue mana in its mana cost, maybe...  \n  \nI play a couple of copy in my Izzet deck, and it perform quite well, in the late game.   \n  \n3.5/5  \n  \nEdit: WOW! With my vote, now its rating is 3.333, with 33 votes! Perfect!",
