      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost206460\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl07_post\">Nice card, and a lot of sinergy with <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Niv-Mizzet\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Niv-Mizzet\">Niv-Mizzet</a>, obviously...! Maybe a cost of <img align=\"absbottom\" alt=\"Variable Colorless\" src=\"/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&amp;name=X&amp;type=symbol\"/><img align=\"absbottom\" alt=\"Blue\" src=\"/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&amp;name=U&amp;type=symbol\"/><img align=\"absbottom\" alt=\"Red\" src=\"/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&amp;name=R&amp;type=symbol\"/> wouldn't have made it overpowered, I think. Sadly, because I like it very much! Maybe if they had included a third choise, like \"or gain control of target creature with converted mana cost X or less.\", and ability that Blue and Red share, even if in red is only until end of turn but since there are 2 blue mana in its mana cost, maybe...<br/><br/>I play a couple of copy in my Izzet deck, and it perform quite well, in the late game. <br/><br/>3.5/5<br/><br/>Edit: WOW! With my vote, now its rating is 3.333, with 33 votes! Perfect!</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl07_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl07_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '206460'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy822\"